\c 10
\s Akaipa anozvikudza pamberi paMwari, asi Jehovha ndiye murwiri
\p
\v 1 Munomirireiko kure, Jehovha? Munozvivanzireiko panguva dzokutambudzika?
\v 2 Pakuzvikudza kwake akaipa anotambudza murombo zvikuru; ngavabatwe namano avakafunga.
\v 3 Nokuti wakaipa anozvirumbidza pamusoro pezvinoda moyo wake, anoruchiva unotuka nokuzvidza Jehovha.
\v 4 Nokuzvikudza kwechiso chake, wakaipa anoti haangabvunzi. Mwari haamo mundangariro dzake dzese.
\v 5 Nzira dzake dzakasimba nguva dzese; zvamunotonga imwi zviri kure kumusoro, haazvioni; kana vari vadzivisi vake vese, anovashora.
\v 6 Anoti mumoyo make, handingazununguswi; handingavi panhamo kusvikira kumarudzi angu ese.
\v 7 Muromo wake uzere nokutuka nokunyengera nokumanikidza; zvakashata nezvakaipa zviri pasi porurimi rwake.
\v 8 Anogara panzvimbo dzokuvanda dzemisha; pakavanda ndipo paanouraya asina mhosva; meso ake anovandira asina wokumubatsira.
\v 9 Anovandira pakavanda seshumba panzvimbo yayo; anovanda kuti abate murombo; anobata murombo, kana achimukakatira mumumbure wake.
\v 10 Anonyangira, anokambaira pasi, varombo vanowiswa nevanesimba vake.
\v 11 Anoti mumoyo make: Mwari akanganwa; anovanza chiso chake, haangatongozvioni.
\p
\v 12 Simukai Jehovha; Mwari simudzai ruoko rwenyu; regai kukanganwa varombo.
\v 13 Akaipa anozvidzireiko Mwari, achiti mumoyo wake: Hangabvunzi?
\v 14 Mazviona henyu; nokuti munoona zvakaipa nokutambudzika muchizviisa muruoko rwenyu; asinamubatsiri anozviisa kwamuri; makava mubatsiri wenherera.
\v 15 Vhunai ruoko rwowakaipa. Kana ari munhu akashata, nzverai zvakaipa zvake, kusvikira musingazozviwani.
\v 16 Jehovha ndiye Mambo nokusingaperi-peri; vahedheni vakaparadzwa munyika yake.
\v 17 Jehovha, makanzwa zvinodikanwa navanyoro; muchasimbisa moyo yavo, mucharerekera nzeve yenyu;
\v 18 kuti mutongere nherera neanotambudzwa, kuti munhu wapanyika arege kuramba achivhundusa.
